snippet.title: ATOMINE - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
BUY ATOMINE ON STEAM:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/603100/ATOMINE/

ATOMINE is a twin stick procedural shooter roguelite set in a virtual world with minimalist design, where the player recounts on the screen the real events of STUXNET, the first weapon ever created in the form of computer virus.
